> ::Zardus::
> 
> Zardus nods, frowning. A spark container wasn't in any way 
important, since there were many in the lab, but why would Orchestra 
want one? Zardus didn't really believe the bot's exuse of research, 
but he didn't see anything bad about sparing one for better relations 
with the Predacons.
>

to go."
> 
> He looks at Wheeljack. "You can give him one of the spark 
containers in the equipment room next to here. If something comes up, 
contact me."
> 
> Zardus turns around, leaving the room and heading for the docking 
bay.
>
